# Card with floors and room selection. You can also pick how many times do you want to clean each room... You must activate/tap the room to enable and be cleaned.
# You should create:
#  - input_boolean for each droom to enable the room clean;
#  - counter for each room to select how many cleans will be made;
#  - scripts for each folder (check scripts in this repository);


